Privacy Policy for EvolveSMS Themes from Father Son Apps on the Google Play Store

This privacy policy governs your use of the software application EvolveSMS Theme ("Application") for mobile devices that was created by Father Son Apps.
The Application is a theme for EvolveSMS, an SMS app that is not owned by Father Son Apps.

What information does the Application obtain and how is it used?
  The Application does not obtain any information from you or your device. The Application is mainly an app of resources for images to use in EvolveSMS.
  The Application does not collect, store, or share any personal data or device information.

Do third parties see and/or have access to information obtained by the Application?
  No. The Application does not collect any information, so no third parties can see or have access to any information obtained by the Application.

What are my opt-out rights?
  You can stop using the Application at any time by uninstalling it from your device.

Changes
  This Privacy Policy may be updated from time to time for any reason.
  We will notify you of any changes to our Privacy Policy by posting the new Privacy Policy here.
  You are advised to consult this Privacy Policy regularly for any changes, as continued use is deemed approval of all changes.

Contact us
  If you have any questions regarding privacy while using the Application, or have questions about our practices, please contact us via email at sparetimeapps @gmail.com.
